{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2341938a21","title":"关于发布通报问题致中南、华东、西南军区电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d7a4eb7b4a","index":0,"year":1950,"month":11,"day":23,"articleId":"2341938a21"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"b88ee9ae06","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2341938a21","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中国人民解放军中南军区剩通报第二号，主要讲湖南军区部队于10月中旬重点进湘西南的靖县、绥宁及雪峰山地区的土，另以一部并湖北一个团配合西南军区西阳军分区会川湘鄂边龙山地区土，至11月上旬止，经一个月进已基本上告一段落。"}],"contents":[{"id":"dead25b493","type":"title","text":"关于发布剩菲通报问题致中南、华东、西南军区电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2341938a21"},{"id":"b88ee9ae06","type":"paragraph","text":"中南军区，华东军区，西南军区：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2341938a21"},{"id":"86157b9d36","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）中南剩通报第二号收到，甚好。（二）你们三大军区各有土能若十万均待限期剩绝，建议华东军区仿照西南、中南两军区办法，每月发布一次内部的剩通报。你们三大军区的期能通报，除发给所属各省各军及我们外，同时发给其他两大军区以资观摩比较。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2341938a21"},{"id":"b245bbc4f2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2341938a21"},{"id":"d31257240c","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月廿三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2341938a21"}],"page":{"id":"0e3a075a3f","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2341938a21","start":388,"end":388}}}},"__N_SSG":true}